OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer
OL,8,FSix people have been killed and
OL,9,Fhundreds injured in New Caledonia -
OL,10,Fthe French Pacific territory that has
OL,11,Fbeen gripped by days of deadly armed
OL,12,Fclashes, looting, and arson.
OL,14,FOn Thursday, French President met with
OL,15,Flocal officials in New Caledonia in a
OL,16,Fshow of support.
OL,18,FPresident Macron opened the meeting by
OL,19,Fcalling for a minute's silence for
OL,20,Fthose killed in shootings, and read
OL,21,Fout their names.
