OL,6,FHe said he viewed a return to calm as
OL,7,Fthe top priority and pledged that
OL,8,Freinforced police forces battling
OL,9,Fdeadly unrest on the French Pacific
OL,10,Farchipelago "will stay as long as
OL,11,Fnecessary."
OL,13,F"I will be very clear here. These
OL,14,Fforces will remain as long as
OL,15,Fnecessary. Even during the Olympic
OL,16,FGames and Paralympics," which open in
OL,17,FParis on Friday July 26, the French
OL,18,Fpresident said.
