OL,6,FPro-independence Kanak leaders, who a
OL,7,Fweek earlier had declined President
OL,8,FMacron's offer of talks by video,
OL,9,Fturned out on Thursday to greet him in
OL,10,Fperson, at a meeting in the capital,
OL,11,FNoumea.
OL,13,FWhere is New Caledonia?
OL,15,FNew Caledonia is a group of islands in
OL,16,Fthe , lying between Australia and New
OL,17,FZealand, with a population of 270,000
OL,18,Fpeople.
