OL,6,FIt was the biggest threat to French
OL,7,Frule in the islands' history, quelled
OL,8,Fby a series of agreements outlining a
OL,9,Fpath to gradual autonomy for the
OL,10,FKanaks.
OL,12,FBut it wasn't until 2018 that the
OL,13,Ffirst independence referendum was held
OL,14,Fon the islands. Three referendums have
OL,15,Fnow been held, with the anti-
OL,16,Findependence side winning out each
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/15
