OL,6,FStill, pro-independence leaders have
OL,7,Fcalled for another vote, arguing that
OL,8,Fthe third referendum should have been
OL,9,Fdelayed.
OL,11,FMany Kanaks were prohibited from
OL,12,Fvoting in the 2021 vote by mourning
OL,13,Fcustoms, following a coronavirus
OL,14,Foutbreak that devastated communities
OL,15,Fthere.
OL,17,FWhy is it important to France?
OL,19,FThe calculus in France has changed in
OL,20,Frecent years, as the south-pacific
OL,21,Fregion takes up a more .
