OL,6,Ffor influence in the region
OL,7,Fintensifies, French officials fear
OL,8,Fthat China could gain sway in an
OL,9,Findependent New Caledonia - just as it
OL,10,Fhas sought to do in the Solomon
OL,11,FIslands.
OL,13,FNew Caledonia is also one of the
OL,14,Fworld's biggest nickel producers,
OL,15,Fholding between 20-30% of the world's
OL,16,Freserves.
OL,18,FPresident Macron visited the islands
OL,19,Flast July to emphasise his vision for
OL,20,Fthe French-Pacific outpost.
