OL,6,F"New Caledonia is French because it
OL,7,Fhas chosen to remain French," Mr
OL,8,FMacron told the crowd. "No going back.
OL,9,FNo stuttering."
OL,11,FWhat has sparked the recent violence?
OL,13,FThe latest period of unrest erupted on
OL,14,FMay 13, when French lawmakers in Paris
OL,15,Fdebated making changes to New
OL,16,FCaledonian voting lists.
