OL,6,FThe French National Assembly approved
OL,7,Fa bill that would, among other
OL,8,Fchanges, allow residents who have
OL,9,Flived in New Caledonia for 10 years or
OL,10,Fmore to cast ballots in provincial
OL,11,Felections.
OL,13,FOpponents say the measure will benefit
OL,14,Fpro-France politicians, and further
OL,15,Fmarginalise the Kanaks by
OL,17,FUnder prior accords, voting in
OL,18,Fprovincial elections was restricted to
OL,19,Fthose who had resided in New Caledonia
OL,20,Fsince before 1998, and their
OL,21,Fdescendants.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/15
