OL,6,FThe measure was aimed at giving
OL,7,Fgreater representation to the Kanaks
OL,8,Fwho had, at that point, become a
OL,9,Fminority group on the islands.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, Paris declared a 12-day
OL,12,Fminimum state of emergency on the
OL,13,Fislands, and rushed in over 1,000
OL,14,Freinforcements to bolster security
OL,15,Fforces that had lost control of parts
OL,16,Fof the capital, Noumea.
OL,18,FAt least six people have been killed,
OL,19,Fincluding two police officers.
