OL,6,FParts of the city have become no-go
OL,7,Fzones, with buildings torched, shops
OL,8,Fpillages, and makeshift barricades set
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,F"The protests reveal the determination
OL,12,Fof our young people to no longer let
OL,13,FFrance rule them," said Daniel Goa,
OL,14,Fthe president of the pro-independence
OL,15,FCaledonian Union party, although he
OL,16,Fcalled for a stop to the violence.
OL,18,FWhat happens next?
