OL,6,FWith police given emergency powers and
OL,7,Fa 6pm to 6am curfew in effect, French
OL,8,Fauthorities say security forces are
OL,9,Fstarting to contain the unrest.
OL,11,FA priority for French authorities has
OL,12,Fbeen clearing the highway to the
OL,13,Finternational airport, in order to
OL,14,Fallow stranded tourists to leave.
OL,16,FAustralia and New Zealand sent planes
OL,17,Fto New Caledonia on Tuesday to begin
OL,18,Fbringing citizens home. Some 300
OL,19,FAustralians and 50 New Zealanders are
OL,20,Fcurrently stranded
