OL,6,FPresident Macron's visit will aim to
OL,7,Fsubdue tensions. He will travel to the
OL,8,Fislands on Tuesday evening, but no
OL,9,Fdetails have been given regarding the
OL,10,Flength of his stay.
OL,12,F"Faced with the outbreak of violence,
OL,13,Fthe priority is the return of order to
OL,14,Fallow dialogue to resume," said a
OL,15,FFrench government spokesperson.
OL,17,F"We are clear: much remains to be done
OL,18,Fbefore the return to normal. The
OL,19,Fgovernment is fully mobilised."
