OL,7,Fcalm, with the High Commissioner of
OL,8,Fthe Republic, Louis Le Franc, warning
OL,9,Fthe territory is "heading straight for
OL,10,Fa civil war".
OL,12,FFrench said re-establishing order was
OL,13,Fnecessary for further dialogue to
OL,14,Fbegin.
OL,16,FBut pro-independence parties say they
OL,17,Fwant the French government to withdraw
OL,18,Fthe reforms before they restart talks.
